{"tid":1941620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"周庭又直播喇","createTime":"2020-03-24T13:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T11:05:10.000Z","uid":229510,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd9fa7623901244f341dcc6afe64bfb634bb5802","tid":1941620,"uid":229510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"又直播喇（最近功課忙, 無出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eART2nv9T0c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeART2nv9T0c&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=090a21b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eART2nv9T0c</a><br />\n<br />\n一有肺炎就會黃標, 記住keep住睇黃Youtuber, 得閒洗下YouTube版, 嚴肅對待黃標問題<br />\n<br />\n每日推<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">周庭</span></strong></span>姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到超越大J成為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港第一</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐今日無新影片<br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐最新影片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JRcmGBpAPNg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJRcmGBpAPNg&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=cdd5a890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JRcmGBpAPNg</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>YouTube</strong></span> channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=b283e537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>Twitter</strong></span></span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchowtingagnes%3Fs%3D09&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=16155727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>Instagram</strong></span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/chowtingagnes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fchowtingagnes&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=79dedea9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/chowtingagnes</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭姐姐<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Facebook</strong></span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/agneschowting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fagneschowting&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=0ed73391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/agneschowting</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>周庭姐姐 宇宙最高</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nユーチューブの中国検閲者は新型コロナウイルスに関する動画に黄色アイコンが付いてました、黄色アイコン付いてる動画がアド出るのこと難しいになる<br />\n<br />\nこれは香港だけの悩みではなく、日本ユーチューバーが黄色アイコンでマークされるの可能性も高い、だから香港人と共に、ユーチューブに圧力をかけてください<br />\n<br />\nこのポストは<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>周庭</strong></span></span>お姉さんが<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港一</strong></span></span>のユーチゥーバーなりるまでに、毎日周庭お姉さんのこと押します<br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さん今日に新しい動画がいませんでした<br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さん最新動画:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JRcmGBpAPNg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJRcmGBpAPNg&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=cdd5a890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JRcmGBpAPNg</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さん<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>ユーチューブ</strong></span> チャンネル:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=b283e537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYstQdiN4QR-EgclyZ4IDfQ</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さん<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>ツイッター</strong></span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchowtingagnes%3Fs%3D09&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=16155727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chowtingagnes?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さん<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>インスタグラム</strong></span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/chowtingagnes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fchowtingagnes&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=79dedea9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/chowtingagnes</a><br />\n<br />\n周庭お姉さん<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>フェイスブック</strong></span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/agneschowting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fagneschowting&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ2qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=0ed73391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/agneschowting</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\